1e9XxW-qYN9E_1loge3igoDqLxAeTXzZB6hrmr6SpWOn1_BToOHfBK7sM1CpZsJ7Rx8cHpVs6sxXr-nfv9K5veHR1pGUEfHA\u0026amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AFemail?__eep__=6\u0026amp;__cft__[0]=AZXHHMObJ4qC-03yJwZBJsfaqWrOU1iYNbHoI4o6eFWf-vgN8nf7HoAtj9YLigQq7glwh5HFadnT4G1e9XxW-qYN9E_1loge3igoDqLxAeTXzZB6hrmr6SpWOn1_BToOHfBK7sM1CpZsJ7Rx8cHpVs6sxXr-nfv9K5veHR1pGUEfHA\u0026amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" data-mce-tabindex=\"0\"\u003e#東華Email\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e，並請注意信箱容量，以接收考試相關訊息。本次考試僅能以東華E-mail及EnglishScore 發送之 Connect Code 應考.\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\"\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e因測驗有 24 小時內 2 次考試，28 天內 10 次考試的限制，如需事先練習，可先以其它帳號登入，以免短時間多次練習考後被系統鎖住，練習考時不用輸入Connect Code。並於正式考試時使用東華E-mail及 EnglishScore 發送之 Connect Code 應考。\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\"\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e考試時間約為40分鐘，測驗結束即可獲得分數。考試帳號有限，報名前請確定當天可以完成考試，報名後請不要缺考，以有效利用考試資源。再請報考同學配合。本次考試僅能以東華E-mail及EnglishScore 發送之 Connect Code 應考.\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\"\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e如通過本測驗達 CEFR B1 (含)以上，由語言中心認證考生身份、學生及考試測驗專屬代碼無誤後登錄，不需另外申請成績證書。\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\"\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-bogus=\"1\"/\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"html-span xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xgzva0m xhhsvwb xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"xz74otr\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t5c/1/16/1f5d3.png\" alt=\"🗓\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" data-mce-src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t5c/1/16/1f5d3.png\"/\u003e\u003c/span\u003e校園考場次(線上)\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e【考試時間】 10/19 (六)\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e【報名期間】 即日起至9/19\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e【報名連結】 \u003cspan class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 x1fey0fg\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2F6femcb%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0VBi0xi7RmVn6evtDDdJILFnPNffiTp8Rt9Z_Vu3tX98F7SFeARSMofg4_aem_3wZoxJJHXmfeogGkuFY4ng\u0026amp;h=AT2HfOu6qjdb3kpDQBGmXU_Qi4xZxF925oI9WL99mg99A4avv-2sck6dA-SAPBiO4BJ81V2HU3bxIctqOMZxAxxU3CZDE_khIfuGg7uFJn30u5xjqsWTGg00B-R8ggPuRp8qO6rgSEpripzvs9x_\u0026amp;__tn__=-UK-R\u0026amp;c[0]=AT2224mS_H6iGtFG4TdzXIK1ipxU8FqtikEy2RGciAi0UkGIGrhZysVTSzwwUjWqpaTBfBKRrJMIS-DN9hPEGIOLXXqaLaZ5oYzGU-S2YCW4-JeckO26Yg1fYFViVopNmbLNOD8tpSOWZcB5n_yJFYqaG4boTIc_4bAT6ev1qvTYIdTp-ZQeyw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" data-mce-href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2F6femcb%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0VBi0xi7RmVn6evtDDdJILFnPNffiTp8Rt9Z_Vu3tX98F7SFeARSMofg4_aem_3wZoxJJHXmfeogGkuFY4ng\u0026amp;h=AT2HfOu6qjdb3kpDQBGmXU_Qi4xZxF925oI9WL99mg99A4avv-2sck6dA-SAPBiO4BJ81V2HU3bxIctqOMZxAxxU3CZDE_khIfuGg7uFJn30u5xjqsWTGg00B-R8ggPuRp8qO6rgSEpripzvs9x_\u0026amp;__tn__=-UK-R\u0026amp;c[0]=AT2224mS_H6iGtFG4TdzXIK1ipxU8FqtikEy2RGciAi0UkGIGrhZysVTSzwwUjWqpaTBfBKRrJMIS-DN9hPEGIOLXXqaLaZ5oYzGU-S2YCW4-JeckO26Yg1fYFViVopNmbLNOD8tpSOWZcB5n_yJFYqaG4boTIc_4bAT6ev1qvTYIdTp-ZQeyw\" data-mce-tabindex=\"0\"\u003ehttps://pse.is/6femcb\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\"\u003e更多說明請至考試網頁查詢。 \u003cspan class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"x1i10hfl